Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, so you've been staying here since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought all this from your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're more suited to travelling than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried because you didn't come yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad that I wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wished?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wished upon the stardust that you would come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Breakfast, breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, show some restraint!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.55,0:00:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you wait for me this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, I had a little errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still have those dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, it was a dream of a forest at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking to someone in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but there was someone snuggled beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked that person, "What's an ocean?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, that person told me lots about the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really fun just talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so fun that I wanted to wrap up the words and store them forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was that fun, sleep forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Gao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A fan, a fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How did your puppet show go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Well... Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki Yukito, you good-for-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who eats for free shouldn't talk so conceitedly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaaaaaat did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing, eating, and sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in a really enviable situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, I dreamed about my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, I often sat here, watching the stars with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a dream of those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In each and every star, there exists a god watching over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They also clean the souls of those who watch the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A short time after that, my father left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After my younger sister died, my father and mother started to quarrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your father now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He married another woman in a faraway town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When we parted, he gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you have to work now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking a short rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Minagi has run away from home now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you try to hide it, I can tell, because I'm a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good being like this, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi has to wake up from her dream now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko pika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for having caused you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Please don't hesitate to come again if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She's starting to remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she lost something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She came to receive an examination because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I replied that she would eventually remember when she found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to Minagi-san's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've... decided to leave this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've stayed here way too long;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's time for me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I... see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come with me, Tohno?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show you the world, the real world, not a dream world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The world?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go together to discover that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we go,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to leave a message for Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We've finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru said that she doesn't want to see a sad-looking Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, decide by your own will what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want, you can really go on a journey with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you... to some other place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The choice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let your own will decide for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars are brilliant today too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that Minagi is watching the stars too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably with her mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I... have to go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's quite late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want, I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have... a home to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In the sky, there's a really sad-looking girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl always sees just sad dreams and has nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't become happy, so she can do nothing but see sad dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,On her back, there are wounded feathers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,feathers with a really mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're packed with the memories of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I had her share one of them with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because there was someone I wanted to meet and comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I thought that if that person became happy, the girl who lives in the sky could become happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans can't live without memories, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, they can't live on memories alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to awaken from your dreams eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because dreams you don't awaken from eventually become sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to go return the feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad to say goodbye to everyone, but because I'm just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because stars have to disappear when the sun rises...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a fragment of a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My being here is just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, it was a really fun dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Michiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't allowed to be born into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I met Michiru for the first time... at that station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day, I went to pick up my father at the station, even after he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Father had already quit his job, but there was nothing else I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it around then that your mother began to call you Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But my mother laughed when I acted as Michiru, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hijiri said that you stopped smiling as much from then on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an afternoon in summer, after a rain shower had ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that I had met her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that she was always nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything started from my sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't wished for a younger sister, no one would have had to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I might even hurt Michiru now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, I want to let someone very important catch at least one glimpse of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan, if you don't hurry, we won't get places for the fireworks competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You were probably tired from playing all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you eat dinner at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At your... house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare for my daughter to bring a friend home, so I made it with the utmost care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even asked about your name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is... Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're called Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a really good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl really loved hamburgers from when she was little too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She always said that if she has a younger sister someday, she'd want her to eat Mummy's hamburgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Minagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Michiru-chan, the hamburgers will get cold, so eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You love them too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are they good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they're really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I invented these hamburgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I taught Minagi how to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be very happy if you eat lots of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:15:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll hold on to this for you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Treat it with care, okay, Minagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, without even saying goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not loo late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There should still be time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because the stars aren't out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru is probably there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous there, so come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't, because I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:17:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been lots of fun up till now, so I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make a face like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi, you have to be smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else I'll be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I... was able to be myself thanks to you, Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave, I probably won't be able to laugh ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi, you can laugh with people other than me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Minagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki Yukito,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,let's make a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl with wings continues to dream sad dreams above the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go back to where she is before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the fun memories you guys gave me to where that girl is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find her, I want you to tell her many more fun stories and free her from her sad dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi, always smile, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile and say "bye bye," okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't smile and say goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...because I won't be able to see you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because even if you awaken from a dream, the memories will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Make your memories with me happy, forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because this is something that only you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi, it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you smiling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue to smile and say "bye bye."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you smiling, Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying goodbye isn't painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be nice if everyone could live smiling all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The world would be full of many smiles, and everyone would be warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't run away from home again, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A rice ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a letter from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He asks if I want to see him this summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:20:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, it seems that I have a younger sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a girl born to my father and his current wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl... Her name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Truthfully, I was a little hesitant, but I've decided to go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother recommended it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a meaning for wings that cannot fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a precious memory of when you once flew in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You like... bubbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:21:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But but... I can't blow them well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do you want me to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, um!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.92,Note,,0,0,0,,[Sign: I'm working hard on my homework]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:21:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:21:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not by coincidence that I started seeing dreams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that this year's summer was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I would do my best to make a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I met you and started seeing those dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:23:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably all connected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I wanted to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make this summer the happiest,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's the summer that I met you, Yukito-san.
